							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The Clara's line of mitigation debuffs will shorten fights enough to keep Bria's from being critical.  Debuffing is HUGE in long battles in this game and arguably the one and only reason why people would ever prefer a dirge over a troub.  Well, that and run speed.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.mausturm.com/EQ2/images/dingsig1.jpg"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
