I already see many things I wish were fixed myself.  Our spells don't scale well at all with most of our buffs being pointless to raise past Adept 1 if even to that point.  I hear that we loose some considerable damage compared to other classes in the 45+ game as well which I hope gets fixed with the Combat Updates.  We also have some serious power issues which I've suffered from the entire game which I hope might get looked at though I doubt it.  (been killing in Ferrott ever chance I get now for Robe of Invoker quest starter...)
<br />

<br />
In the end though at this point I'm seriously happy with the class regardless of the flaws that I see.  I don't want to be a leech not helping my groups either.  But I have seen pretty much no evidence that it is happening at this point and I'm just tired of seeing the same exact people on the official boards and these repeatedly harping on how we should all just quit now.  
<br />

<br />
It's so bad that people actually make posts saying 'Any hope for Dirges in sight?' on the official boards like we suck...  That's all this campaign of spam is really doing.  Helping to convince other classes that we actually are so broke as to not be grouped with.<br />_________________<br /><A HREF="http://eq2players.station.sony.com/en/pplayer.vm?characterId=191894106">Weep</A>
